{"tid":1209966,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有公務員到場聲援：自己首先是香港人然後才是公務員","createTime":"2019-06-12T12:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T12:52:36.000Z","uid":41404,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f233615176a4b66557ece248d66be5a6485bc5d5","tid":1209966,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:42:47.000Z","msg":"金鐘、中環一帶有示威者聚集，亦有現職公務員到場聲援。<br />\n<br />\n公務員黃先生說，今天是第一次走到示威前線。他說，很多示威者表示沒有看到警方驅散前作出警告，無法想像警方有這些行為。<br />\n<br />\n對於警方使用橡膠子彈和布袋彈，他說仍然相信和平示威，由2014年至今，5年來警察武力已升級，又認為示威者與警方相距甚遠，警方不會受到傷害。<br />\n<br />\n被問到作為公務員參與示威會否擔心有後果，黃先生說不顧得那麼多，有些時需要走出來，自己首先是香港人，然後才是公務員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462446-20190612.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462446-20190612.htm&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfItE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=0725af53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462446-20190612.htm&h=0ac1e9f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462446-20190612.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f32e0b20291844352cdc497a3d8439efe8f208a5","tid":1209966,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02a3b16b42d4a00fc62e1e55b09b246fe7179af","tid":1209966,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:44:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccffb20728bda5db467fdd6d1264f48cff8b3361","tid":1209966,"uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"其實有唔少"},{"pid":"f9570f07763b929fb8641ca8eabcbe9f6626c426","tid":1209966,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:47:01.000Z","msg":"香港同外國公務員, 唔小都係好憎政府<br />\n<br />\n唔似得大陸咁, 公務員要黨員先可以做<br />\n所以大陸公務員全部都係中共走狗"},{"pid":"b2f704fee86193ad72391cd4b4418c31f